-350-all-models-ranking-now-available/|dead-url=no}} ''Between 2011 and 2012 a total of 5,017 Peugeot iOns, 4977 Citroën C-Zeros and 4,244 Mitsubishi i MiEVs were sold in Europe.''</ref>。而世界上销量最高的[[插电式混合动力汽车|插电式混合动力汽车]]是[[雪佛兰沃蓝达|雪佛兰沃蓝达]](Chevy Volt)，它和它的姐妹车型Opel/Vauxhall Ampera在北美和欧洲已经卖出了大约44,000辆。销量第二高的是[[丰田普锐斯|丰田普锐斯]](Toyota Prius )插电式混合动力汽车，截至2013年3月已在日本、北美和欧洲卖出超过32,700辆<ref name=TMC5miHEVs>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2013/04/tmc-20130417.html|title=Toyota cumulative global hybrid sales pass 5M, nearly 2M in US|author=Toyota Press Room|publisher=[[Green_Car_Congress|Green Car Congress]]|date=2013-04-17|accessdate=2013-04-17|archive-date=2013-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422004054/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2013/04/tmc-20130417.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

